Interface IRequiredValueFlagNodeItem

  • All Superinterfaces:

    public interface IRequiredValueFlagNodeItem
extends IFlagNodeItem, IRequiredValueNodeItem
    This marker interface indicates that the IFlagNodeItem must have a value to exist.
